## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **epinephrine IM 0.3 mg classical 표준 + neffy nasal 2023 Aug FDA** = first non-injection anaphylaxis. 단점 = nasal congestion 시 absorption 변동. quantum-VQE 의 nasal-mucosa 흡수 + α1/β2 binding 의 path (단 receptor pharmacology 이미 well-known — quantum 의의 = 신규 nasal scaffold delivery).
2. **glucagon nasal Baqsimi 2019 Jul** = first non-injection glucagon (Lilly). caregiver burden ↓ — 의식저하 환자 즉시 사용. dasiglucagon Zegalogue 2021 = ready-to-use autoinjector. quantum-VQE 의 glucagon-R nasal-absorption 가 의의.
3. **sugammadex 2015 Dec FDA (Bridion, Merck)** = γ-cyclodextrin host-guest selective rocuronium/vecuronium 격리. 첫 selective NMBA reversal, neostigmine + glycopyrrolate 대체. quantum-VQE 의 host-guest cavity 적합 — 본 entry initial novel candidate hxq-em-sugammadex-001 motivation.
4. **vasopressin ACLS 2010-2020 → 2020 ACLS removed (epi-only)** = clinical evidence shift example. PARAMEDIC2 2018 RCT — epinephrine outcome modest (ROSC ↑ but neuro-favorable survival 미개선). quantum 외부 — clinical RCT 정책 결정 영역.
5. **amiodarone vs lidocaine VT/VF** = ALPS trial 2016 (NEJM) — 동등, 2018 ACLS lidocaine 재도입. quantum-VQE 의 hERG off-target + Na/K channel selectivity discrimination 이론적 가능.
6. **naloxone Narcan OTC 2023 Mar + nalmefene Opvee 2023 May** = OTC accessibility 가 fentanyl epidemic 응답 (cross-substance_use). nalmefene 긴 half-life vs naloxone 짧은 half-life — fentanyl 재반동 (re-narcotization) 회피. quantum-VQE 의 μ-OR binding-residence-time path.
7. **ketamine NMDA 응급** = Ketalar IM/IV 1970 — RSI 표준 + 응급 진통. ketamine intranasal trauma pediatric research (PICU/ED off-label 광범위). hemodynamic-stable advantage (etomidate adrenal-suppression 우려). quantum-VQE 의 NMDA enantiomer (R-ketamine 항우울 vs S-ketamine 마취) 의 path.
8. **CroFab 2000 + Anavip 2015 (crotalidae antivenom)** = North American pit viper. Anavip = Bioclon Mexican-imported F(ab')₂ (긴 half-life — 재독 회피). 2023+ Mexican-imported antivenom research 확장. quantum-VQE 의 신규 anti-venom Fab interface 가 의의 (snake-venom heterogeneity 한계).
9. **patiromer 2015 + sodium zirconium cyclosilicate (Lokelma) 2018** = hyperkalemia binder generation. Lokelma 1-hr onset — ED-suitable (vs patiromer 7-hr 만성). insulin/dextrose + calcium gluconate 표준 supplement. quantum-VQE 의 selective K+ binder pocket (Na+ off-target 회피) 의 path.
10. **TXA tranexamic acid CRASH-2 (2010 trauma) / CRASH-3 (2019 TBI) / WOMAN (2017 PPH) / 2020 FDA postpartum hemorrhage** = lysine analog antifibrinolytic. 응급 출혈 + trauma + PPH 광범위. quantum-VQE 의 plasminogen lysine-pocket binding 이미 well-known — 신규 selective 의의 한정.
11. **응급 시간 scale (1–60 분) = VIROCAPSID + RIBOZYME 한계** — AAV transduction 일/주 단위, mRNA translation 시간 단위. 응급의학 axis = QUANTUM (small-molecule) + WEAVE (nasal scaffold) + NANOBOT (absorption) 위주. honest scope 한계.
12. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, 응급의학 임상 의미 한정. 응급은 prehospital protocol + EMS training + system-level intervention 기여 큼 — pharmacology 단독 한계.

